name: Nicky's Thai Kitchen
notes: Great Thai food. There is outside seating that is fantastic for nice days. Easy date night place. Casual attire is fine but the dining room is looks nice enough for more formal evenings. If you want beer or wine with your meal, bring your own in a cooler! No corkage fees.

name: Cap't Con's Fishhouse
notes: Best bacon-cheeseburger in Lee County. I order the "Cap't Bacon Burger" with onion rings.
